title: What the heck is PulseChainArt?
content: PulseChainArt are randomly generated, non-fungible tokens, also known as an “NFT”. Owners gain access to community benefits such as additional FREE NFTs and crypto related raffles and prizes. There are 10,000 PulseChainArt and each is completely unique. No two are the same. They were generated from a smart contract using over 75 different traits. PulseChainArt are minted, stored, and traded on the Ethereum blockchain.

title: How do I purchase PulseChainArt?
content: You can purchase a PulseChainArt on this website by scrolling to the top and clicking “Start Mint Now”.

title: When is the public sale?
content: Our current launch date is June 1st, 2022

title: Are some more rare than the others?
content: Every PulseChainArt has unique traits/attributes, but some traits are rarer than others. For example, some have Hats, but only a few dozen have a particular hat - even fewer will be found “On Toast”. You can see the traits for a PulseChainArt under “properties” on OpenSea OR you can look at a third-party tool such as Rarity Tools.
